description:
The excel file contains the Ct values obtained in the different reactions of real time quantitative PCR for 9 microRNAs (cel-miR-39-3p, miRNA-16,  &nbsp; miR-27a-3p ,  miR-93-5p ,  miRNA-103 ,  miRNA-132 ,  miRNA-142, miR-146a  and  miRNA-574) in plasma exosomes of dogs with epilepsy and controls. 
 This is complementary data to the manuscript:  Analysis of plasma-derived exosomal microRNAs as potential biomarkers for canine idiopathic epilepsy.&nbsp;  
 &nbsp;

